components.content:
I certify that all statements made in this application are true and complete to the best of my knowledge. I also understand that any false statement or omissions in this application will result in my application being rejected. Lastly, I understand and agree that completion of this online application does not guarantee acceptance into the summer employment program but enters me into the citywide SYEP lottery.

Agree by entering your SSN and Date of Birth below, checking the box and clicking "' Agree". If the Social Security Number you provide is incorrect, your application will be considered incomplete and you will be prohibited from participating in SYEP.
